-We need to bring all the products from the db an display them in ManageProducts.js
-We will implement update and delete



1-Go into the apiAdmin

-To perform crud on product we need:

get all products
get a single product
update single product
delete single product

// GET ALL
// reuse the getCategories and modify for GET ALL
// name: getProducts
// params: none
// fetch: `{API}/products`
// keep the rest the same

// DELETE A PRODUCT
// reuse the updateOrderStatus
// name: deleteProduct
// params: productId, userId, token
// fetch: `{API}/product/${productId}/${userId}`
//Method: DELETE
// headers
// do not send anything in the body (remove it)

// GET A SINGLE PRODUCT
// reuse the getProducts
// name: getProduct
// params: productId
// fetch: `{API}/product/${productId}`
//Method: DELETE
// headers
// do not send anything in the body (remove it)

// UPDATE A PRODUCT
// reuse the deleteProduct
// name: updateProduct
// params: productId, userId, token, product
// fetch: `{API}/product/${productId}/${userId}`
//Method: PUT
// headers: remove Content-Type
// we need body: product

